('90672','31224','5','New villa in Sol de Mallorca with 3 bedrooms for sale '),
('90673','31225','5','Sol de Mallorca is located in the municipality of Calvia on the south-west coast of Majorca. \r\nThe villa was built 2013/14 and stands on a 1.224m ² plot. The 260m² of living space spread over 2 floors. The ground floor offers:  entrance, living-dining room, open plan kitchen, guest bedroom with en suite bathroom and guest toilet. \r\nOn the 1st floor are 2 more bedrooms, each with en suite bathroom and a large terrace. \r\nThe high quality equipment includes, a stylish fitted kitchen (with Cornue gasoven), pvc double glazed windows, white doors, parquet floors, air conditioning h / c, solar assisted heat pump for hot water and heating (radiators), solar pool heating, etc. \r\nThe basement with underground parking for several cars are available including space for a guest apartment or wellness. \r\nA covered terrace, a low-maintenance landscaped garden and swimming pool invite you to relax.\r\n'),
